To use:

sh get_ic.sh

and then start the simulation as normal.

Simulation is public at:

https://www.ics.uzh.ch/~aurel/euclid.htm

IC files are from:
https://www.ics.uzh.ch/~aurel/euclidIC_2048/

Converted to bigfile using the script in
tools/convert_from_gadget_1.py

From Aurel's site:

COSMOLOGICAL PARAMETERS FOR THE REFERENCE RUN
(L=500 Mpc/h, N=2048^3)

Omega_m = 0.3071
Omega_l = 0.6929
Omega_b = 0.0483
ns      = 0.9611
sigma8  = 0.8288
H0      = 67.77
